description: The investment seeks investment results that correspond to the price and yield performance, before fees and expenses, of the MorningstarÂ Developed Markets ex-US Factor Tilt Hedged IndexSM. The index reflects the performance of a selection of companies that, in aggregate, possess greater exposure to size and value factors relative to the Morningstar Developed Markets ex-US Index, and hedges the currency-related risk of the securities included in the index against the U.S. dollar on a monthly basis. The fund invests at least 80% of its total assets in the securities of the index and in ADRs and GDRs based on the securities in the index. It is non-diversified.
name: FlexShares Currency Hedged Morningstar DM ex-US Factor Tilt Index Fund
